---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Domain Availability Checker - Free & Fast" description="Quickly check if a domain is available. No signup required. Learn how to avoid false positives and pick better names.">
  <section class="container-pad">
    <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-3">
      <ol class="flex gap-2 items-center">
        <li><a href="/" class="hover:underline">Home</a></li>
        <li>/</li>
        <li aria-current="page">Domain Availability Checker</li>
      </ol>
    </nav>
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4">Domain Availability Checker</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-700 max-w-2xl mb-6">Use our fast, simple checker to see if your domain is free. Then read our guides to choose a stronger name and register it for the right price.</p>
    <a href="/#check" class="btn-primary inline-block px-6 py-3">Go to Checker</a>
    <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <a href="/blog/how-to-check-domain-availability-smart-way" class="card p-5 hover:shadow-xl transition text-left">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-lg">Check Availability the Smart Way</h2>
        <p class="text-white/75 text-sm">Avoid false positives and move fast when a name is free.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog/best-domain-name-tools-for-beginners" class="card p-5 hover:shadow-xl transition text-left">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-lg">Best Tools for Beginners</h2>
        <p class="text-white/75 text-sm">Free and low-cost tools to research names quickly.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog/top-domaining-tools-for-investors-2025" class="card p-5 hover:shadow-xl transition text-left">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-lg">Top Domaining Tools for Investors</h2>
        <p class="text-white/75 text-sm">Find expired, brandable, and SEO-ready names faster.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
